snippet.title: Synth Riders - "Power-Ups" for Multiplayer [Release Trailer]
snippet.description:
Experience "Power-Ups" - a free update that brings the fun of Kart racer-style boosts and attacks to the Multiplayer Mode of Synth Riders!


Trailer song: “New Game” by Nitro Fun (Cyberpunk Essentials DLC)
Players: Deckpaint, Emikodo, Haselnuss, HeyFalcon, Qalvael, SpiritChunker, Touge, Wirrel, Xypher Orion
--------------------------------------
Synth Riders is available on Oculus Quest & Rift, Steam #VR & Viveport: http://bit.ly/playsr
Join the Synth Riders Discord Community: http://discord.synthridersvr.com/
Official website: https://synthridersvr.com/


Follow #SynthRiders:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/synthridersvr
Facebook: http://fb.me/synthridersvr
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/synthridersvr/
